      <title>耐克的销售预警导致摩根士丹利、摩根大通等暂停股票买入评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/nike-nke-sales-warning-leads-morgan-stanley-jpmorgan-and-more-to-downgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[耐克公司 (Nike Inc.) 警告未来一年业绩将放缓，此举促使大批分析师撤回对该股的买入评级，自 2017 年以来，华尔街对该公司股票的看涨情绪降至最低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/nike-nke-sales-warning-leads-morgan-stanley-jpmorgan-and-more-to-downgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 14:26:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国债市场涨势在盈利季度最后一天停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/treasuries-advance-after-key-inflation-data-matches-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债收益率的上涨势头在六月的最后一个交易日丧失了动力，在债券指数重新平衡的最后一个小时交易中延续了涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/treasuries-advance-after-key-inflation-data-matches-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 12:44:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
